### 1. Create a user
POST http://localhost:4000/api/prediction/create/user/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "08012345678",
  "pin": "1234",
  "confirm_pin": "1234"
}
### 2. Validation check - mismatched PINs should FAIL
POST http://localhost:4000/api/prediction/create/user/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "08099999999",
  "pin": "1234",
  "confirm_pin": "0000"
}

### 3. Login - returns a token
POST http://localhost:4000/api/prediction/login/user/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "08012345678",
  "pin": "1234"
}
